parameters: 舞台灯光打开的声音，然后观众欢呼，然后 出现Live 弹唱的BGM
Let me see, let me see!
The first show is a performance by the band of class 202-1
第一个节目是202-1班的乐队表演
Being able to form a band from a single class is really impressive
一个班级里面能组出一个乐队真是厉害呢
Oh oh, but I heard that the K-ON Club is helping them externally
哦哦，不过听说好像是与轻音部的外援
The live scene looks really amazing
Our class, class 901's performance is third in line, The Adventures of The Man From Little Organ Star
我们901班的节目是第三个，《小风琴星人历险记》
I heard that the one starring as the female protagonist had also gotten a cold recently
听说表演女主角的同学最近也是得了重感冒
Think it was Yan Cheng, our male protagonist and screenwriter, who also wasn't very happy with the end result
而且好像晏城同学，我们这次节目的编剧和男主角，也不是很满意最后的效果
Even though I haven't participated much before, feels like I've heard quite a bit of news about this over the past two days
虽然之前一直没怎么参与，但感觉这两天道听途说的消息还挺多的
But it might be because I haven't helped with anything, I feel a bit guilty
不过也可能是因为自己啥都没帮上，心里有些愧疚感
After all... Even Ari, who doesn't talk much, has gone to help...
毕竟……连不怎么说话的雅莉同学都去帮忙了……
(Ari is totally focused on the show)
(雅莉同学聚精会神地看着节目)
(She usually hides under those big round glasses)
(平时一直躲在大圆框眼镜下的她)
(At this moment, she is showing her smart eyes without reservation)
(此刻毫无保留展露着她那双灵动的双眼)
I heard that if it weren't for what happened in the past few days...
听说如果不是因为前几天的事情……
Ari would also have been participating in the performance...
雅莉同学也会作为群演上台参与节目来着……
Ari... I really wish to help her if I could
雅莉同学……如果可以的话真希望能帮到她
It feels like... in a strange way I can understand her feelings
总觉得……自己在莫名其妙的地方能够体会到她的感受
Saying it like that makes me feel like a hentai, hahaha... hahaha...
这么说感觉自己像个变态，哈哈哈……哈哈哈……
Not that I know her well...
Guess I'll start by mixing with her?
果然还是要从混熟开始吧？
From tomorrow onwards, I've assigned myself a task
明天开始，就给自己一个任务
"Ah, nice to meet you, it's our first time meeting. I'm your classmate, Shio~" Like that?
“啊，你好，初次见面，我是和你同班的汐哦~” 这样吗？
Why would classmates even need to introduce each other as classmates!
为什么同班同学还要介绍自己是同班同学啊喂！
The next performance is our class's The Adventures of The Man From Little Organ Star
下一个节目是我们班的《小风琴星人历险记》
Yan Cheng is performing as the male protagonist, but honestly...
晏城表演了男主角，但是说实话……
The interaction with the female protagonist couldn't be any harder...
和女主角的互动简直不能再生硬了……
Sure enough, tacit understanding needs a lot of time to cultivate...
果然默契还是很需要花时间培养的呢……
The Blackboard News Selection comes after the class stage performances
班级舞台剧表演之后是黑板报评选
Class 101 got first place this year
我们班嘛……肯定是没有的了
After announcing the results of the Blackboard News Selection, the principal gave a brief summary of the school festival
宣布完黑板报评选结果，校长对校园祭作了简单的陈词总结之后
After that, all events ended with this year's school festival
再之后，整场活动，连同今年的校园祭一起结束了
The principal announced we could head home early today, so I went home alone
校长说今天提早放学，所以就自己一个人回了家
On the way home, I kept thinking about Ari's situation, and unknowingly reached the door to my house...
回家的时候一直想着雅莉同学的事情，结果不知不觉中已经走到家门口……
